Title: SMASH: Smoothing using Adaptive Shrinkage
Version: 1.1-0
Date: 2018-03-22
Description: Smash performs univariate signal denoising/nonparametric
    regression for Poisson distributed data or Gaussian distributed data with
    possibly heteroskedastic error terms.
